{"tid":2453672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國將就國籍法進行1983年以來第一次改革","createTime":"2021-03-19T15:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T00:43:50.000Z","uid":53844,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4a927ea4f3dd88d54cd69e391b024eead444b785","tid":2453672,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:17:12.000Z","msg":"A Home Office source said: &ldquo;British nationality law has not changed significantly since 1983. It is outdated, convoluted and littered with anomalies which impact hundreds of people each year. <br />\n<br />\nThese new reforms will bring about lasting change to our entire immigration system, ensuring it is fair and just.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n英國內政部的消息人士說：&ldquo;自1983年以來，英國國籍法並沒有發生太大變化。它已經過時、令人費解並且導致到處都是由此衍生出來的異常現象，每年影響數以百計的人。<br />\n<br />\n這些新的改革將為我們的整個移民制度帶來持久的變化，確保它是公正和公正的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe reforms, which will be introduced as part of changes to immigration legislation, will add flexibility into the system, so that the Home Office can waive residence requirements in exceptional cases, the source said.<br />\n<br />\n消息人士說，這些改革將作為移民立法改革的一部分而引入，將增加該體系的靈活性，以便內政部在特殊情況下可以免除居住要求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/mar/18/british-nationality-law-reform-aims-to-remove-windrush-anomalies\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fuk-news%2F2021%2Fmar%2F18%2Fbritish-nationality-law-reform-aims-to-remove-windrush-anomalies&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=a489a262\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/mar/18/british-nationality-law-reform-aims-to-remove-windrush-anomalies</a>"},{"pid":"b6ccfd2aee07f0420b508de259b46a8b950f6799","tid":2453672,"uid":33556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a